		<title>Curso Teologia e Capelania(Em Breve)</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://sala.inppnet.com.br/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=143:curso-basico-de-parapsicologia&amp;catid=86&amp;Itemid=522"/>
